{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-55","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 55","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Naučio sam da je <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span> pomoćni glagol koji pomaže u postavljanju pitanja. Takođe si naučio da kada želiš da pitaš o nečemu specifičnom, možeš koristiti reč za pitanje <span class=\"highlighted-text\">what</span>.</p>\n<p>Kada želite pitati o poslu ili ulozi osobe, koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">what</span> zajedno sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span> da napravite pitanje. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">What do you do?</span> znači <span class=\"highlighted-text\">What is your job?</span>.</p>\n<p>Kada govoriš o drugoj osobi kao što je Marija, kažeš <span class=\"highlighted-text\">What does she do?</span> zato što <span class=\"highlighted-text\">she</span> je treće lice jednine imenice (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">she</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">he</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">it</span>), i sa ovim rečima/imenicama, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span> se menja u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">does</span>.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Popunite praznine da biste napravili pitanje o radu Marije koristeći pomoćni glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span>.</p>\n</section>","explanation":null,"challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"English","superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","block":"learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","lang":"en-US","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-55"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>What BLANK Maria BLANK?</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"does","feedback":"<p>Ovo je glagolska struktura <span class=\"highlighted-text\">do</span>, koja se koristi zajedno sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">he</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">she</span>, ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">it</span>.</p>"},{"answer":"do","feedback":"<p>To je glavni glagol koji se koristi u pitanjima koja pitaju o poslu ili svakodnevnim aktivnostima neke osobe.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":null,"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","dashedName":"task-55","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-56","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-54","id":"657cd143f74299f36a624c7a","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":22,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-conversation-starters-in-the-break-room/task-55"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}